      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If you know ahead of time which languages the user needs to translate,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "you can prompt them to download those languages in advance by calling this method.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When you call this method the framework asks the user for permission to download the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Translation/documentation/Translation/TranslationSession/sourceLanguage",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Translation/documentation/Translation/TranslationSession/targetLanguage",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "If the languages are already installed or are in the middle of downloading, the function returns",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "without prompting the user.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "If you call this function when the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "sourceLanguage",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " is ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "nil",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", it throws",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Translation/documentation/Translation/TranslationError/unableToIdentifyLanguage",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " since there’s no sample text to",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "identify which source language to use for translation.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
